No. 08-1509. Classen Immunotherapies, Inc., Petitioner v. Biogen IDEC, et al. 561 U.S. 1040, 130 S. Ct. 3541,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1119,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5533. June 29, 2010.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and *1120case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Federal Circuit for further consideration in light of Bilski v. Kappos, 561 U.S. 593, 130 S. Ct. 3218, 177 L. Ed. 2d 792 (2010).

Same case below, 304 Fed. Appx. 866.
